fields.name: description
fields.value: Complete list of companies in BC who have been triggered by the NSC system to receive an NSC warning letter, safety plan assessment letter, or have been triggered for audit or compliance review by the NSC system in September 2024. Provide list with the company names and the type of action triggered. The system automatically triggers these lists on the 1st of every month, for the entire month. This search request will cover the entire list of triggered companies for these months. The request should also cover all carriers that the system triggered for audit in during these months who have not yet received their demographics letters. (Date Range for Record Search: From 9/1/2024 To 9/1/2024)

fields.value: E&N Railway Remediation Report by Thurber Engineering commissioned by MoTI for the Island Rail Corridor planning group studies. This study was shared with the Nanaimo Regional District in February 2024 and used in the study group, particularly for the Snaw-naw-as land reversion of the rail land within their reservation.
